Collaborative filtering is one way to approach the problem. This has been(or still is)
used at Amazon and many other systems including first version of Google News back in 2007.

Amazon Paper : http://www.cs.umd.edu/~samir/498/Amazon-Recommendations.pdf
Google News   : http://www2007.org/papers/paper570.pdf
Summary :  Edwin Chen's answer https://www.quora.com/How-does-Amazons-collaborative-filtering-recommendation-engine-work
Example(with code) : http://aimotion.blogspot.com/2009/11/collaborative-filtering-implementation.html
Tool : Apache Mahout (http://mahout.apache.org/users/recommender/recommender-documentation.html)

Other References:
A great class on Recommender systems : https://www.coursera.org/learn/recommender-systems/outline
